        <h1>media query eye for the straight bi | using tailwindcss daisyui</h1>

        If not blatantly obvious, the <span
            class="tooltip tooltip-bottom badge text-xs bg-primary"
            data-tip="this is a badge">badges</span
        > represent standard <code>media query</code> demarcations:

        <ul>
            <li>
                <span
                    class="tooltip tooltip-bottom badge bg-primary text-xs"
                    data-tip="mobile">PH</span
                >: <code>mobile</code>
            </li>
